title.narrative: Guinea-Bissau: Emergency Electricity and Water Rehabilitation Project

description.narrative: The development objective of the Emergency Electricity and Water Rehabilitation Project (EEWRP) is to assist the Government of theRepublic of Guinea Bissau (GoGB) in the rapid restoration and improvement of electricity and water supply services in its capital city.
